<div ng-app="" ng-controller="creatorAddTrainingController" class="container">

    <strong class="error">{{ error }}</strong>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        INFORMACJE O SZKOLENIU
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        *Utworzenie szkolenia nie jest trudne, ale jesli robisz to pierwszy raz lub chcesz przypomniec sobie caly proces skorzystaj z przewodnika z zakladce jak stworzyc szkolenia
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        NAZWA SZKOLENIA
        <input type="text" name="currentTraining.Name" ng-model="currentTraining.Name" />
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        OPIS SZKOLENIA
        <input type="text" name="currentTraining.Description" ng-model="currentTraining.Description" />
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        Grafika obrazujaca szkolenie [400 x 300px i nie wieksza niz 350kb]
        <div id="inputButto" ng-click="loadImage()">
            Wczytaj
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        *Nie przejmuj sie, nie misisz dodawac zadnej grafiki! Jesli nie dodasz zadnej grafiki zostanie uzyta grafika domyslna
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        Ile procent punktow jest niezbednych do zaliczenia Twojego szkolenia?
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        *Domyslnie ustalilismy 80% ale mozesz zmienic wartosc wybierajac inna możliwosc
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        <input type="radio" name="passResult" ng-model="currentTraining.PassResult" value="100" />100%
        <input type="radio" name="passResult" ng-model="currentTraining.PassResult" value="80" />80%
        <input type="radio" name="passResult" ng-model="currentTraining.PassResult" value="65" />65%
        <input type="radio" name="passResult" ng-model="currentTraining.PassResult" value="50" />50%
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        Komunikat, ktory zobacza uzytkownicy ktorzy zalicza kurs (osiagna wymagana liczbe punktow) Przykladowy komunikat "W wyniku szkolenia zdobyles wiedze na temat procedury/produktu"
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        <input type="text" />
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        I na koniec wybierz oznake ktora otrzyma uzytkownik, ktory ukonczy z powodzeniem to szkolenie
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        Wczytaj wlasna [musi byc 100px na 100px i nie wiekszy niz 150kb] lub wybierz ktoras z przygotowanych przez nas!
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        <div id="inputButto" ng-click="loadIcon()">
            Wgraj wlasna
        </div>
        <div id="inputButto" ng-click="showIcon()">
            Wybierz z listy
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        ZAWARTOSC SZKOLENIA
    </div>

    <tabset>
        <tab heading="dodaj tekst">
            <input type="text" ng-model="currentDetail.Text" name="currentDetail.Text" />
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="cancel(currentDetail, 0)">
                    Anuluj
                </div>
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="add(currentDetail, 0)">
                    Zapisz
                </div>
            </div>
        </tab>
        <tab heading="dodaj grafike">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                wczytaj grafike lub upusc ja na pole obok lub podaj link
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="upload(currentDetail, 1)">
                    Wczytaj grafike
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                Podaj link: <input type="text" ng-model="currentDetail.ExternalResource" name="currentDetail.ExternalResource" />
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="cancel(currentDetail, 1)">
                    Anuluj
                </div>
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="add(currentDetail, 1)">
                    Zapisz
                </div>
            </div>
        </tab>
        <tab heading="dodaj wideo">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                Wczytaj film przerzuc i opusc go na pole obok lub podaj link
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="upload(currentDetail, 2)">
                    Wczytaj film
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                Podal link do YT lub vimeo <input type="text" ng-model="currentDetail.ExternalResource" name="currentDetail.ExternalResource" />
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="cancel(currentDetail, 2)">
                    Anuluj
                </div>
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="add(currentDetail, 2)">
                    Zapisz
                </div>
            </div>
        </tab>
        <tab heading="dodaj prezentacje">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                Wgraj prezentacje (ppt, pptx, pdf)
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="upload(currentDetail, 3)">
                    Wybierz plik
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="cancel(currentDetail, 3)">
                    Anuluj
                </div>
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="add(currentDetail, 3)">
                    Zapisz
                </div>
            </div>
        </tab>
        <tab heading="dodaj plik">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <div id="simpleRow">
                    Wgraj plik
                </div>
                <div id="simpleRow">
                    <div id="inputButto" ng-click="upload(currentDetail, 4)">
                        Wybierz plik
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="cancel(currentDetail, 4)">
                    Anuluj
                </div>
                <div id="inputButto" ng-click="add(currentDetail, 4)">
                    Zapisz
                </div>
            </div>
        </tab>
    </tabset>

    <div ng-repeat="item in trainingDetails">
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="detailUp(item)">
                UP
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="detailDown(item)">
                DOWN
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="detailEdit(item)">
                EDIT
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="detailDelete(item)">
                REMOVE
            </div>
        </div>

        <div ng-show="item.ResourceType == 0">
            <div id="simpleRow" ng-hide="item.isEdit">
                {{item.Text}}
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                <input type="text" ng-model="item.Text" name="item.Text" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div ng-show="item.ResourceType == 1">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                pole z grafika
            </div>
        </div>
        <div ng-show="item.ResourceType == 2">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                pole z wideo
            </div>
        </div>
        <div ng-show="item.ResourceType == 3">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                pole z prezentacja
            </div>
        </div>
        <div ng-show="item.ResourceType == 4">
            <div id="simpleRow">
                pole z plikiem
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="simpleRow">
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="detailSave(item)" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                ZAPISZ
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="detailCancel(item)" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                ANULUJ
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        PYTANIE W SZKOLENIU
    </div>
    <div ng-repeat="item in trainingQuestion">
        <div id="simpleRow">
            Pytanie {{trainingQuestion.length}}
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="questionUP(item)">
                UP
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="questionDown(item)">
                DOWN
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="questionEdit(item)">
                EDIT
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="questionDelete(item)">
                REMOVE
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="questionSave(item)" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                ZAPISZ
            </div>
            <div id="inputButto" ng-click="questionCancel(item)" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                ANULUJ
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="item.Type == 0">

            <div id="simpleRow" ng-hide="item.isEdit">
                {{item.Text}}
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" name="item.Text" ng-model="item.Text">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].Score">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[1].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[1].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[1].Score">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[2].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[2].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[2].Score">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[3].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[3].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[3].Score">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="item.Type == 1">
            <div id="simpleRow" ng-hide="item.isEdit">
                {{item.Text}}
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" name="item.Text" ng-model="item.Text">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].Score">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[1].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[1].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[1].Score">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[2].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[2].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[2].Score">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[3].IsSelected" />

                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[3].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[3].Score">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="item.Type == 2">
            <div id="simpleRow" ng-hide="item.isEdit">
                {{item.Text}}
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="item.isEdit">
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" name="item.Text" ng-model="item.Text">
            </div>
            <div id="simpleRow">
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].Text">
                Punkty
                <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-disabled="!item.isEdit" ng-model="item.Answers[0].Score">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="simpleRow">
        Pytanie {{trainingQuestion.length + 1}}
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="selectedQuestion == 1">
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" name="currentQuestion.Text" ng-model="currentQuestion.Text">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].Score">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[1].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[1].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[1].Score">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[2].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[2].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[2].Score">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="radio" name="answer" value=true ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[3].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[3].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[3].Score">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="selectedQuestion == 2">
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" name="currentQuestion.Text" ng-model="currentQuestion.Text">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].Score">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[1].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[1].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[1].Score">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[2].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[2].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[2].Score">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="checkbox" name="answer" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[3].IsSelected" />

            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[3].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[3].Score">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow" ng-show="selectedQuestion == 3">
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" name="currentQuestion.Text" ng-model="currentQuestion.Text">
        </div>
        <div id="simpleRow">
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].Text">
            Punkty
            <input type="text" id="mainInput" ng-model="currentQuestion.Answers[0].Score">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        <div id="inputButto" ng-click="nextQuestion()">
            Dodaj kolejne pytanie
        </div>
        <select ng-model="selected" ng-options="c for c in questionType" ng-show="showQuestionType" ng-change="changeQuestion(selected)">
            <option value="">Wybierz</option>
        </select>
    </div>

    <div id="simpleRow">
        OKRESL DLA KOGO MA BYC WIDOCZNE SZKOLENIE
    </div>
    <div id="simpleRow">
        Na ta chwile polecamy Ci nie zaznaczac zadnej grupy. W takiej sytuacji kurs bedzie widoczny tylko dla Ciebie. Polecamy Ci go uruchomić i przetestowac a dopiero pozniej przyznac uprawnienia dla innych uzytkownikow (Mozesz to zrobic w zakladce moje szkolenia)
    </div>
    <div ng-repeat="item in Groups">
        <input type="checkbox" ng-model="item.selected" />{{item.Name}}
    </div>
    <div id="simpleRow">
        <div id="inputButto" ng-click="save()">
            ZAPISZ SZKOLENIE
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
